        <detaileddescription>
<para>Issues the XENMEM_acquire_resource hypercall to map a resource buffer (e.g., I/O request server, grant table, VM trace buffer) into the specified domain&apos;s physmap, or query its total size.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
