</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>nr_frames</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>[in,out] On input, number of frames to map; on return, number of frames actually mapped (or total frames if queried). </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
